		<div id="choice">
			
			<h3>Editor&#8217;s Choice</h3>
			
			<p class="info">originally ran: October 24, 2005</p>
			
			<h4 class="title"><a href="http://www.alistapart.com/articles/zombiecopy/" title="Attack of the Zombie Copy">Attack of the Zombie Copy</a></h4>
			<h5 class="byline">by 
	
	<a href="http://www.alistapart.com/authors/k/erinkissane"> Erin Kissane</a>
	
</h5>
			
			<p>You&#8217;ve seen them around the web, these zombie sentences. They&#8217;re not hard to recognize: syntax slack and drooling, clauses empty of everything but a terrible hunger for human brains. Here&#8217;s how to fight back. </p>
			
		</div>
		
		
